# AI SDLC — Project Configuration

## Core Settings

ticketing: github-issues # none | jira | github-issues
branch_base: staging # base branch all new work branches from (staging | main | master)

## GitHub

owner: thuva-agentic # e.g. my-org
repo: notes # e.g. my-api

## Jira

# Required when ticketing: jira. Leave blank otherwise.

cloud_id: {your-atlassian-cloud-id} # e.g. 26be6ccf-8778-4a20-9584-98afaab9eba7
project_key: {your-project-key} # e.g. ENG, DM, WEB

## GitHub Issues

# Required when ticketing: github-issues. Uses owner/repo from GitHub section above.

github_username: thuva-agentic

## None

# When ticketing: none, all ticket steps are skipped.

# Branches are named from descriptions only.

# The full dev loop (spec, plan, implement) still works without a ticketing system.
